{"tid":2019726,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民悼梁凌杰逝世11個月","createTime":"2020-05-16T13:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T14:12:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"275dba94cde4f1e39e7b5f91c74b938e4c42442f","tid":2019726,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:17:17.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200516/I5HY4DO52TF7MHXT2VM3AFOYUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200516%2FI5HY4DO52TF7MHXT2VM3AFOYUQ%2F&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BaWONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=b8cb20a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200516%2FI5HY4DO52TF7MHXT2VM3AFOYUQ%2F&h=e29c9e79\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200516/I5HY4DO52TF7MHXT2VM3AFOYUQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n市民悼梁凌杰逝世11個月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200516/large/1589560278_ba3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200516%2Flarge%2F1589560278_ba3e.jpg&h=f70a84be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民燃點燭光悼念梁凌杰。何家達攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年6月15日，梁凌杰（35歲）不滿政府拒撤回《逃犯條例》修訂，在金鐘太古廣場以死相諫、墮下身亡。昨日梁凌杰逝世11個月，本港荒誕消息卻接踵而至，但港人未忘初心自發悼念梁凌杰，自傍晚起早有市民在金鐘放置鮮花築成白色花海。惟數十警員繼續藉防疫規例警告打壓，無故拉起封鎖線，又繼續驅逐記者，更有失控警員與記者及區議員爭執。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警一度設封鎖線<br />\n<br />\n昨午1時，多名巿民在中環置地廣場舉行悼念會，各人在商場各層高呼「光復香港，時代革命」等抗爭口號。至傍晚6時半，第二場悼念會在太古廣場舉行，數十市民自發聚集廣場中庭，有穿上黃雨衣的市民揮動旗幟及舉起五大訴求，缺一不可的手勢，更有巿民在梁墮樓位置獻上白花，並放置紙板連儂牆，各人貼上「未敢忘記」、「條路再難行，我們會代你走下去」等標語。<br />\n<br />\n在場市民自律地以八人一組，但警員卻設封鎖線，喝令市民記者後退。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者盧珮瑤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200516/large/1589560276_44f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200516%2Flarge%2F1589560276_44f5.jpg&h=af39259a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批市民聚集金鐘高呼抗爭口號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200516/large/1589560277_8a1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200516%2Flarge%2F1589560277_8a1d.jpg&h=a837fc33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有穿黃雨衣市民在太古廣場中庭舉起五一手勢。"},{"pid":"307705fd833d3ff7bbf5058393bb9883f8b29945","tid":2019726,"uid":75655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"64 手足唔會忘記 抗日手足唔會忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb8e9ce3a8e97074e3e9da0f290b9902a014c46","tid":2019726,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HaExOas.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHaExOas.jpg&h=1e6c722b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8ed8a58476b66c821390c42aaf227fd2b4fa187","tid":2019726,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eb8e9ce3a8e97074e3e9da0f290b9902a014c46","tid":2019726,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HaExOas.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHaExOas.jpg&h=1e6c722b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><b